      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIJINKERY (2) was far too good after leading making it three straight, scoring by 5 lengths (22.69) at this track over 400m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. The hardest to beat again. ZINFANDEL DASH (8) was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where she gave a sight, finishing second (19.66) and beaten 3 lengths over 342m at Angle Park. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Can measure up. BACARDI GIRL (7) scored two back in the quickest time on the program then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 10 length 5th at Sandown (35.10). Some good form is emerging from her last run. Worth another chance. NEON BLUE (5) won last start after racing on the pace. Big chance on that form.",
